article_title: How A Couple Of 'Frugal Weirdos' Are Saving 71% Of Their Income So They Can Retire At Age 33

article_metadata.description: A young, Boston couple had enough of their 9-5 desk jobs, so they're super-charging their savings to retire to Vermont before their 35th birthdays.
article_metadata.author: Lauren Gensler
